description: Both verse 1 and verse 2 are short four measures, they currently have 12 measures each but should have 16 instead. In the version of the song before my revisions, verse 1 lasted from the 6th measure to the 17th measure and verse 2 from the 30th measure to the 41st measure. After my revisions verse 1 now lasts from the 6th measure to the 21st, and verse 2 lasts from the 34th measure to the 49th
title: West Coast Smoker
